            <h2>Goofy Speedway Teleport Trick</h2>
            <p>
                New toon? Go to Goofy's Speedway to gain teleport access. A toon can then get back to Toontown Central 
                quickly by teleporting to Goofy Speedway and using the tunnel to the playground.
            </p>
        </details>
