            <summary id="12">Tips for Kart Racing</summary>
            <h2>Quickly Earning Sweeping Race Trophies</h2>
            <p>
                Sometimes earning those pesky sweeping trophies is a pain. A clever way to earn sweeping trophies
                is to swap sweeping wins with another toon. This way there is no stress or pressure to win 3
                races in a row, and you and your toon friend benefit from the deal!
            </p>
